name: Davis Shoup
bio: Hi, I'm Davis! I'm a creative, hardworking and dedicated software developer currently taking on a Software Engineering Immersive bootcamp at General Assembly. I come from a manufacturing background where I spent seven years in the industry. During that time, I was promoted five consecutive times and landed a position as a supervisor. I'm motivated by results and eager to put this mindset towards my next position in the software development industry.
